code: import axios from'axios';export class ContactService{static getGroups(){let dataURL="".concat(this.serverURL,"/groups");return axios.get(dataURL);}static creatContact(contact){let dataURL="".concat(this.serverURL,"/contacts");return axios.post(dataURL,contact);}static getGroup(contact){let groupId=contact.groupId;let dataURL="".concat(this.serverURL,"/groups/").concat(groupId);return axios.get(dataURL);}static getAllContacts(){let dataURL="".concat(this.serverURL,"/contacts");return axios.get(dataURL);}static getContact(contactId){let dataURL="".concat(this.serverURL,"/contacts/").concat(contactId);return axios.get(dataURL);}static updateContact(contact,contactId){let dataURL="".concat(this.serverURL,"/contacts/").concat(contactId);return axios.put(dataURL,contact);}static deleteContact(contactId){let dataURL="".concat(this.serverURL,"/contacts/").concat(contactId);return axios.delete(dataURL);}}ContactService.serverURL='http://localhost:9000';
